title: [LucarioPK Subs] Detective Conan 706 - Bourbon Figures it Out
description: After the intense situation the Mystery Train brought upon Conan and the others, an outing that was meant to be relaxing turns sour when a Black Organization member appears. What is Bourbon's objective? Furthermore, when a man is killed out of revenge for a former mutual friend's death, when the dust settles, who did it? The puzzle is solved by none other than Bourbon, but why? Find out this week in Detective Conan 706 - Bourbon Figures it Out!
